{"tid":630091,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"如果DSE 4 core咁樣改制 大家點睇?","createTime":"2018-04-15T09:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T13:22:07.000Z","uid":103434,"like":0,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5fd6161d31405aecf20b7c0a3f202159d8b0fab9","tid":630091,"uid":103434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:38:06.000Z","msg":"呢排追DSE新聞有感而發 <br />\n假如將DSE 4 core 改成以下format <br />\n大家點睇?<br />\n<br />\n中文、英文、數學照舊<br />\n通識科响學校繼續獨立成科 分一日考<br />\n但係個grade唔會獨立一科計 <br />\n而係報考時將通識併入中、英、數當其中一份extra卷 <br />\n唔分paper grade, 但可以最多+1或-1grade <br />\n好似英文oral IR咁<br />\n最後拉個大grade<br />\n而學校、marker都唔應該知道各個考生點併<br />\n併法唯一條件係中文考通識唔可以併英文 英文考唔可以併中文<br />\n例如我predict中英數4,5,5*<br />\n用英文考LS，咁我申請LS併英文<br />\n最後考得好好 英文5*拉上5**<br />\n或者我predict 3,3,5*<br />\n用中文考LS 申請併入數學<br />\n咁當我操數操到曉飛 然後LS嗰日肚痛交白卷<br />\n數學都只係由5**拖咗落5*<br />\n當然JUPAS唔再有4C+1/2E，而係3C+2/3E<br />\n咁樣可以鼓勵考生讀多個有把握嘅選修科<br />\n文商學生可以操下選修paper 或者谷爆中或英文grade<br />\n理工學生唔怕一個LS拉低4+2分數 安心啲操數<br />\n繼而減少通識科錯配大學學位 同埋確保準大學生嘅術科基礎夠好<br />\n觀迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701a273953bef1b97e139c047df20e0b1a3f2d70","tid":630091,"uid":179571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:39:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8b414520452dca60262638de689035314abae7c","tid":630091,"uid":31314,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"簡單複雜化"},{"pid":"2fc71629d66a41ab9ce0e6e84e9b6530a38603df","tid":630091,"uid":129042,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"唔洗考DSE <br />\n全部變曬大學入學試囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40180968aa8625c60700f28d94849329f9437dbb","tid":630091,"uid":119145,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"你點改計分都好 根本愈黎愈多位又有咩意義？ 諗下點裝備自己好過啦<br />\n<br />\n重點係：依家咁撚多位，正常識講野都入到啦"},{"pid":"54c53c0d6406cec9ec352846366db335155725a1","tid":630091,"uid":25329,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:46:17.000Z","msg":"咁我唔考通識好過 一個grade換幾年青春<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99713ff6454e3e3f1dddf0da133c70657aece8f","tid":630091,"uid":135445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"響呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c2c0f0bd5a37d252503d7965e39034e7045fc7","tid":630091,"uid":135445,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:48:31.000Z","msg":"直接discard左通識就一天都光哂"},{"pid":"1d312eb8ede7b599f2cc56893786f4819411788e","tid":630091,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7c2c0f0bd5a37d252503d7965e39034e7045fc7","tid":630091,"uid":135445,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:48:31.000Z","msg":"直接discard左通識就一天都光哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:56:27.000Z","msg":"discard core please <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5470e0c519c805c0a44ce9723df7df03d7a2848","tid":630091,"uid":70293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"轉做best5, cancel 3322"},{"pid":"c81cc50febec50f6790d0a81cc2ddcd25a991845","tid":630091,"uid":135445,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a5470e0c519c805c0a44ce9723df7df03d7a2848","tid":630091,"uid":70293,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:56:58.000Z","msg":"轉做best5, cancel 3322"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T09:58:59.000Z","msg":"agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" cla